1
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:48,700
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,420 --> 00:00:51,780
=Episode 4=

3
00:01:02,740 --> 00:01:04,100
(Mom)

4
00:01:07,240 --> 00:01:08,799
- Hello?
- Ye Chen,

5
00:01:08,799 --> 00:01:09,880
you have ten minutes.

6
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:12,079
Come to Huaxin Enterprise
on Ping'an Road now.

7
00:01:12,239 --> 00:01:13,159
Huaxin Enterprise?

8
00:01:13,319 --> 00:01:14,079
Alright.

9
00:01:14,079 --> 00:01:15,250
I'll be there in five minutes.

10
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,280
Scammer!

11
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,439
Fraud company!

12
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,760
Give back our hard-earned money!

13
00:01:24,439 --> 00:01:25,239
Scammer!

14
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:26,519
Fraud company!

15
00:01:26,519 --> 00:01:27,790
Give back our hard-earned money!

16
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:28,920
Scam...

17
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:29,239
Wait.

18
00:01:29,319 --> 00:01:30,200
Mom, what's going on?

19
00:01:30,250 --> 00:01:31,280
Why are you only here now?

20
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,480
Didn't you say five minutes?

21
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:33,680
No, I was...

22
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,760
This scam company

23
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,719
promised high interest
with guaranteed returns,

24
00:01:36,719 --> 00:01:39,439
tricking me
into investing all our family's savings!

25
00:01:39,439 --> 00:01:41,840
They're after our principal money!

26
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:44,120
Mrs. Xiao, you don't need
to explain so much to him.

27
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,480
Just tell him to shout.

28
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,319
Why are you here?

29
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:47,319
Mr. Zhang is righteous.

30
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:48,200
He rushed over as soon

31
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,680
as he heard something happened to me.

32
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,280
Not like you!

33
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:51,680
You useless piece of trash!

34
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,159
Shout!

35
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:54,239
Come,take a break.

36
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:55,120
Come here.

37
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:55,719
Rest a bit.

38
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:56,040
Shout!

39
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,400
Lan,

40
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:04,920
this is your useless son-in-law?

41
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,400
Shoo!

42
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:07,990
In a few days
I'll have my daughter divorce him,

43
00:02:08,090 --> 00:02:09,280
then marry Mr. Zhang instead.

44
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:11,120
What are you staring at?

45
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,400
Keep shouting!

46
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:13,599
Louder! Don't slack off!

47
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:14,639
Scammer!

48
00:02:15,250 --> 00:02:16,039
Give back our money!

49
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,120
Louder!

50
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,120
Scammer!

51
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,000
Give back our money!

52
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,400
Scammer!

53
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,220
Give back our money!

54
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,520
The real boss behind Huaxin is Hong Wu,

55
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,800
a big figure in the underworld.

56
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:30,479
- If Mr. Ye keeps going on...
- Scammer!

57
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:31,270
Give back our money!

58
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,990
He might get himself
into serious trouble.

59
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,360
Scammer!

60
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,000
Give back our money!

61
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:40,560
Scam...

62
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:41,360
Scam...

63
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,639
Mom.

64
00:02:44,370 --> 00:02:45,680
Yelling our heads off won't help.

65
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,599
Look at my throat.

66
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:47,990
No one's paying us any attention.

67
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:49,159
You useless trash.

68
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:50,140
You can't even do anything right!

69
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:50,680
Keep shouting!

70
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,919
Mrs. Xiao, to be honest,

71
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:53,660
yelling like this
doesn't hurt them at all,

72
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:54,639
does it?

73
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:55,790
We need to change how we shout.

74
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,520
How we shout?

75
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,199
Shout what?

76
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:57,919
Wait.

77
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,159
You're the famous Mr. Zhang of Jinzhou,
aren't you?

78
00:03:00,159 --> 00:03:01,560
Once you step in,
won't everything be settled?

79
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,680
If you can just get their boss
to come out,

80
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,759
leave the rest to me.

81
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,520
You have a point.

82
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,360
But how exactly should I shout?

83
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,840
I've never dealt
with something like this.

84
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:20,280
Teach me.

85
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:20,960
I'll tell you.

86
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:21,960
Just shout this,

87
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:25,520
"Tell your boss
to get out here right now!"

88
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:28,360
Who's calling for me to get out?

89
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:35,580
(Hong Wu)

90
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,759
You wanted to use me
to do your dirty work,

91
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:41,680
then don't blame me for playing along.

92
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,360
It's him!

93
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:46,000
The legendary Mr. Zhang,

94
00:03:46,420 --> 00:03:47,280
feared across Jinzhou!

95
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,039
No, it's not me!

96
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:50,490
It's fine, Mr. Zhang. Don't be afraid.

97
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,280
All of you!

98
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:53,520
Why aren't you

99
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,719
kneeling and apologizing yet?

100
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,280
He's already said

101
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:58,319
if you don't return the money right now,

102
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:00,120
he'll have you all arrested

103
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:01,199
and sent off to the prison!

104
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:01,990
Don't talk nonsense!

105
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:02,840
It's fine.

106
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:09,039
I am a reasonable man.

107
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,479
You're scared now, aren't you?

108
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,840
You scoundrel!

109
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,879
Return the money now!

110
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:14,520
Or Mr. Zhang will make you regret it!

111
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,130
Just you wait!

112
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:15,719
Mrs. Xiao.

113
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,439
Mrs. Xiao.

114
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:18,319
I didn't say it.

115
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,319
You didn't?

116
00:04:20,280 --> 00:04:21,080
I heard everything

117
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:21,990
and you're still denying it?

118
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,680
How dare you insult Mr. Hong?

119
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,439
You got a death wish?

120
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:27,519
I really didn't say it!

121
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,519
You didn't?

122
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:29,519
You're dead!

123
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,410
I really didn't say it!

124
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:35,120
Did you say it or not?

125
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,079
Did you?

126
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:36,639
And you!

127
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:37,319
Stop!

128
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:40,120
I don't mean you. Just keep going.

129
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,480
Come over here!

130
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,279
Come here!

131
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,120
Not me!

132
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,399
You can't hit my mother-in-law!

133
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:46,199
And who might you be, young man?

134
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:50,680
Ye Chen,

135
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:52,480
son-in-law of the Xiao family.

136
00:04:52,839 --> 00:04:53,879
Ah, so I've heard.

137
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:57,040
Jinzhou's biggest loser.

138
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:01,920
You flatter me.

139
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,550
Didn't expect to be that famous.

140
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,480
I really hate people like you,

141
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:07,480
cowards who hide behind others

142
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,360
and stir up trouble.

143
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,199
Boys,

144
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:11,399
teach him a lesson!

145
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:14,519
Kneel.

146
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,630
If you dare lay a hand on me today,

147
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:21,079
you'll never stand up again.

148
00:05:21,730 --> 00:05:22,480
What did you say?

149
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:25,199
Chop off his arms and legs.

150
00:05:25,210 --> 00:05:26,710
You trained martial arts since young,

151
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,990
and left yourself with complications.

152
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,360
Varicose veins,

153
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:30,959
a herniated disc,

154
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,920
and disrupted blood flow.

155
00:05:32,550 --> 00:05:33,639
That's why you can't stand.

156
00:05:33,639 --> 00:05:34,470
What are you saying?

157
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,519
But I do have a way
to get you back on your feet.

158
00:05:37,759 --> 00:05:42,360
Even the renowned Dr. Shi Tianqi
couldn't fix my back.

159
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:43,759
And you think you can?

160
00:05:44,330 --> 00:05:45,879
If you don't try, how would you know?

161
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:48,759
If you dare mess with me, kid,

162
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:52,120
you'll die right here.

163
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:57,560
Do you still remember
the pressure points I taught you?

164
00:06:15,180 --> 00:06:16,260
(Gate of Origin Shu)

165
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:18,340
(Sea of Qi Shu)

166
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,680
I'll kill you!

167
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,720
- Mr. Hong!
- What are you shouting for?

168
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:40,279
- Mr. Hong!
- Don't touch me.

169
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,720
I'm flattered.

170
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:54,360
Sorry.

171
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,399
One move short.

172
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,439
I'm standing up.

173
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:11,519
Thank you, Master Ye.

174
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:13,079
- Thank you, Master Ye!
- Thank you, Master Ye!

175
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,590
No need for formalities.

176
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,920
Boy,

177
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,360
I never thought

178
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:21,120
I'd be able
to stand again in this lifetime.

179
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:24,120
You're my savior!

180
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,199
From now on, if you ever need anything,

181
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,439
just say the word.

182
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:28,340
I'll make it happen.

183
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:30,199
I don't have anythi...

184
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,759
About my mother-in-law's money...

185
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:34,639
Easy.

186
00:07:35,319 --> 00:07:37,279
I'm a man of reason.

187
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:38,560
This card contains

188
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:40,160
1.3 million in principal

189
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,800
and 200,000 in profit,

190
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,320
making it 1.5 million in total.

191
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:43,959
Take it.

192
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,319
That much?

193
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,920
And here's another 500,000,

194
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:50,040
a small token from me.

195
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,040
Please accept it.

196
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,399
Mom, take it.

197
00:07:57,639 --> 00:07:58,439
Ye Chen...

198
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,399
You've really grown up.

199
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:02,800
Then what about ours?

200
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,920
Enough.

201
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,800
For Chen's sake,

202
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,319
everyone who came today

203
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:11,360
will get their money back,
principal and interest included.

204
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:12,920
- Yay!
- Oh yay!

205
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:15,600
Sorry I misjudged you earlier.

206
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:19,000
Exactly. You're truly impressive
for your age.

207
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:22,279
You're clearly destined for greatness.

208
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,480
I don't deserve such praise.

209
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,810
If you want to thank anyone,
thank Mr. Hong instead.

210
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,480
You're too kind, Chen.

211
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,399
Then, Mr. Hong,

212
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,160
I'll take my leave for now.

213
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:32,399
Come dine at my Weiding Pavilion one day.

214
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:34,360
I'll treat you properly.

215
00:08:34,800 --> 00:08:35,279
Sure.

216
00:08:36,079 --> 00:08:36,639
Come on, Mom.

217
00:08:37,319 --> 00:08:37,759
Chen!

218
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,039
What about this young man here?

219
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:42,840
Harder!

220
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:47,759
Harder.

221
00:08:49,039 --> 00:08:50,879
Trash should stay in the trash can.

222
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,159
OK.

223
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:57,780
(Double Kill)

224
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:05,799
Mr. Tang,

225
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,360
Mr. Ye did very well today.

226
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:09,960
Just small tricks.

227
00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:13,890
And the press conference
the day after tomorrow...

228
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:15,320
Something will definitely happen.

229
00:09:17,639 --> 00:09:18,600
Twenty years.

230
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,399
I've waited a full 20 years.

231
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,639
The real show

232
00:09:24,399 --> 00:09:25,919
is finally about to begin.

233
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:32,600
Look.

234
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,120
Is this outfit okay

235
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:36,039
for your signing ceremony?

236
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:37,559
Mm-hmm.

237
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,200
More than okay.

238
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,200
You look incredibly handsome.

239
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,080
Ye Chen,

240
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,440
tell me honestly.

241
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,679
Did you deliberately
set Zhang Wenhao up?

242
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:52,200
Set up?

243
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,080
There was no setup.

244
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:57,720
I really have to criticize you for this.

245
00:09:58,679 --> 00:09:59,240
Why?

246
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,960
If something like this happens again,

247
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,519
you have to record it

248
00:10:04,519 --> 00:10:05,519
so I can watch too,

249
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:07,390
and see exactly how Zhang Wenhao
gets humiliated.

250
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,279
That was just a warm-up.

251
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,919
I'll put on a big show for you
the day after tomorrow.

252
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,120
So confident?

253
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:12,559
Yeah.

254
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,080
An honor battle.

255
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:14,750
Certain victory.

256
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,440
Ye Chen,

257
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,559
I suddenly feel like

258
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:25,279
you've changed a lot compared to before.

259
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,200
Have I?

260
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,440
Just look at what happened today.

261
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:33,720
How did you suddenly
know medical skills?

262
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,159
Actually...

263
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:41,519
Madam Li wasn't the only person
who raised me up.

264
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,919
There was also Mr. Quan.

265
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:46,840
He was a very mysterious man.

266
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:53,200
The first time I met him,

267
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,519
it was on a pitch-dark night.

268
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,919
His appearance

269
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,840
left a deep impression on me.

270
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,679
He may have looked stern on the outside,

271
00:11:12,159 --> 00:11:14,519
but he taught me many things.

272
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:17,000
He was actually a very kind old man.

273
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,519
But how come

274
00:11:20,519 --> 00:11:21,759
you never mentioned him before?

275
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:24,559
I only remembered it recently.

276
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:29,679
When I was a kid, I got seriously ill.

277
00:11:30,159 --> 00:11:31,639
I almost died back then.

278
00:11:32,159 --> 00:11:33,360
But Madam Li saved me.

279
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:36,440
After I recovered,

280
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:37,440
I realized

281
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:39,120
I forgot everything Mr. Quan taught me.

282
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,000
All that remained

283
00:11:40,020 --> 00:11:41,559
were these pressure-point techniques,

284
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:43,590
and even those work only half the time.

285
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:46,080
Thankfully, they came in handy today.

286
00:11:47,679 --> 00:11:50,039
You must've suffered a lot back then.

287
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:51,720
Of course I did.

288
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,879
It was miserable.

289
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:55,720
Churan,

290
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:59,000
why was my childhood so full
of hardship?

291
00:11:59,000 --> 00:11:59,960
Especially these past few days.

292
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,080
My back aches, my waist hurts,
nothing feels right.

293
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:06,000
And in two days,
something important is coming up.

294
00:12:06,310 --> 00:12:07,990
Just thinking about it
gives me a headache.

295
00:12:08,399 --> 00:12:10,480
Why don't you let me sleep here
for two nights?

296
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:13,399
The bed's pretty comfortable.

297
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:22,159
Where did you say you want to sleep?

298
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:24,159
It's fine to give me just the edge.

299
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,240
Just two nights, okay?

300
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,080
Or maybe a bit longer?

301
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:34,679
So are you sleeping or not?

302
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,399
Yes.

303
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,519
Where?

304
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:43,879
Same place as always.

305
00:12:55,879 --> 00:12:57,320
Grandma, you're arranging flowers?

306
00:12:58,039 --> 00:12:59,519
They're really beautiful.

307
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:00,720
Oh yeah!

308
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,559
The press conference
is all taken care of.

309
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,799
I've already delivered the invitations
to all the major companies

310
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:06,879
and prominent families.

311
00:13:06,879 --> 00:13:08,720
- Mmm hmm.
- Good.

312
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:10,080
Grandma,

313
00:13:10,799 --> 00:13:11,879
are you really

314
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:13,720
going to make Xiao Churan the director?

315
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:14,840
Then

316
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:17,120
what about the two of us?

317
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,919
- Grandma!
- That's right, Grandma!

318
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:22,480
I have my own arrangements.

319
00:13:26,399 --> 00:13:27,000
Ye Chen!

320
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:33,960
Boss.

321
00:13:36,519 --> 00:13:37,639
Boss, don't worry.

322
00:13:37,639 --> 00:13:38,750
I still have another move.

323
00:13:39,159 --> 00:13:40,879
That press conference won't happen.

324
00:13:41,559 --> 00:13:43,840
I will make Ye Chen pay the price.

325
00:14:04,262 --> 00:14:06,750
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

326
00:14:06,837 --> 00:14:10,590
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

327
00:14:11,050 --> 00:14:15,987
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

328
00:14:16,150 --> 00:14:18,437
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

329
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:21,430
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

330
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:25,125
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

331
00:14:25,425 --> 00:14:28,437
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

332
00:14:28,637 --> 00:14:31,687
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

333
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:34,762
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

334
00:14:35,030 --> 00:14:38,187
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

335
00:14:38,412 --> 00:14:42,162
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

336
00:14:42,162 --> 00:14:45,025
♪I belong to no one♪

337
00:14:45,087 --> 00:14:48,537
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

338
00:14:48,537 --> 00:14:51,212
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

339
00:14:51,212 --> 00:14:57,550
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
